name: ConvertTo-ProcessMitigationPolicy
synopsis: Converts an mitigation policy file formats.
description: Converts an EMET policy file or pinning rule file to a new Windows 10 format.

parameters.name: EMETFilePath
parameters.description: File that either contains cert pinning rules or an existing EMET process mitigation configuration file.

parameters.name: OutputFilePath
parameters.description: Resulting new Windows10 process mitigation/pinning rules format.
